    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok that's only because you are using an `<input type=\"checkbox\" />` as a hierarchical facet template. Thus that's a case we did not implement (a list of hierarchical facet using checkboxes), if you use a regular `<a href='#'>` it will be ok.\n\nAnd that's what you should use because it's not very good to use an `<input>` and then force the rendering to looks like it's not an input.\n\nUse a different template for the (hierarchical) menu, that's no big deal and it should be easier to understand for the users in fact.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-08T19:35:20Z",
