  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Labels and checkboxes have a very specific behavior on clicks so we do not handle them when multiple level deep.\n\nThere is no point in using checkboxes for the hierarchical menu. In a menu you NEED links so that you can cooy paste the href and ctrl click to open in a new tab.\n\nIt will in the end look weird to you users to have a hidden checkbox just to avoid having a different template.\n\nYou have two different UI element, you need a different template here.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-08T21:48:17Z",
